<h2><a name="programoverview">Program Overview</a></h2>
<p>The Ricktag®Rewards Program (the “Program”) is a loyalty reward program offered by Ricktag Network Solutions Inc. (“Ricktag”, “us”, “our” or “we”) to customers of Ricktag Partners(the “Partners” or Distributors”) and online at www.ricktag.ca.</p>
<ol>

<li>
<p>The Program allows persons who have completed the membership enrolment steps in accordance with the present Terms and Conditions and who have been issued a Ricktag Rewards Card by a Ricktag Distributor(the “Program Members” or “Members”) to collect Ricktag points or receive discounts at Ricktag Merchants(the “Merchants” or “Stores”) when making purchases in-stores on items identified from time to time by Ricktag (“Eligible Purchases”), and to redeem these Ricktag Points for rewards, benefits and/or rebates offered by Ricktag and its Merchants from time to time.</p>
<p>Ricktag may designate from time to time, partners from whom Members will be able to collect or redeem Ricktag Points in the Program (the “Program Partners” or “Partners”).</p>
<p>Members acquire no vested right or entitlement to the continued availability of any particular reward or benefit, Program Partner or redemption level.</p>
