<h3>Participation in the Program</h3>
<h3><a name="membershipenrolment">Membership Enrolment</a></h3>

<li><p>Membership is free and no initial purchase is required in order to become a Member.</p></li>

<li><p>To enroll, you must have a valid Canadian address and be 16 years of age or older. At a minimum, you must provide your first name, last name, and a valid email address. If you do not have a valid email address, you must provide a valid mailing address and phone number. You may also be asked to provide data such as gender, date of birth and postal code during the sign-up process. Only one Ricktag rewards account (“Ricktag Rewards Account” or “Account”) is permitted per person.</p></li>

<li><p>Only one rewards program account (i.e. one Ricktag Rewards Account) is permitted per person.</p></li>

<li><p>To become a Member, simply ask a Store employee to sign you up or visit <a href="http://www.ricktag.ca/">www.ricktag.ca/</a> and complete the online form. To become a valid Member, you must complete the enrolment process by providing complete and accurate information and indicating your acceptance of these Terms and Conditions. You may be required to register your account to complete the enrolment process within a defined period of time before Reward Points are awarded to your Account.</p></li>

<li><p>After completion, you will receive a rewards member number ("Member Number"). If you sign up in-store, you will be given a card with a unique Member Number (the "Rewards Card" or the "Card").</p></li>

<li><p>The Ricktag Rewards Card is not a credit card. The Card is the property of Ricktag and it may be revoked at any time by Ricktag in the event of breach of the Terms and Conditions of the Program by a Member, misuse or abuse of the Program by a Member, fraud, and/or any other actions deemed by Ricktag to be contrary to the Program or the interests of its Members or Partners.</p></li>

<li><p>Members cannot share their account number and account information with anyone else unless otherwise given permission by Ricktag. Immediate family members are permitted to use the card. Membership benefits apply only to the individual Ricktag Rewards Account holder. Account information, including, but not limited to, the Ricktag Rewards Account password should be protected and kept secure.</p></li>

<li><p>You must advise us immediately of any changes of Personal Information (as defined herein) including name, address, and e-mail address either by visiting www.ricktag.ca or emailing us at customerservice@ricktag.ca. Ricktag shall not be liable for misdirected email or mail communications, including any notices under these Terms and Conditions or any consequences thereof where your Personal Information is inaccurate or no longer valid. If we believe that some of our records are inaccurate, we may contact you to verify our records. We reserve the right to cancel any Account for which we have incomplete or inaccurate Personal Information and all points redemptions on that Account may be blocked and any points awarded may be forfeited. The submission of false or fictitious Personal Information will result in all the Ricktag Points accumulated on an Account being forfeited.</p></li>

<li><p>Ricktag reserves the right to refuse issuance of an Account to any person who does not follow the prescribed enrolment procedures.</p></li>

<li><p>Ricktag rewards membership is only available to individuals. Ricktag rewards membership will not be available to corporations, businesses, charities, partnerships, enterprises, schools or anyone other than an individual, unless written approval is received in advance from Ricktag, in its sole discretion. Ricktag Points will not be awarded if in Ricktag’s reasonable opinion the merchandise purchased will be used for resale or commercial use and any Ricktag Points awarded on such purchases will be forfeited. If a Ricktag rewards Member was awarded points for an offer or promotion in which a Member purchased product in excess of reasonable quantities, the Ricktag Points awarded as a result of that offer or promotion may be forfeited without prior notice and the Account may be suspended or closed.</p></li>

<li>
    <p> a)If for any reason we believe a Member is under the age of 16, we reserve the right to request proof of age. If such proof is not provided, all Personal Information regarding that individual may be deleted from our system and the Membership may be terminated, including the immediate forfeiture of all Ricktag points.</p>
