    <p>b) Ricktag Discounts are not to be combined with any other offers. It is the responsibility of the card-member to visit www.ricktag.ca and login to view all current Merchants and discounts.  When there is a 2-4-1 discount, the free portion applies to the second item only and must be of equal or lessor value of the first item. Third, fourth and fifth items are not discounted and must be purchased at regular price.</p>
