<h3><a name="collectionofmidaspoints">Collection of Points</a></h3>

<li>
    <p>To collect Ricktag Points following enrolment, you must make Eligible Purchases in-store by presenting your personal valid Ricktag Rewards Card. Any unauthorized reproduction of the Ricktag Rewards Card may lead to legal prosecution and forfeiture of all Ricktag Points and membership in the Program.</p>
    <p><strong>At Cash, In-store</strong>: The Member's personal Rewards Card must be presented to the cashier before the Eligible Purchase transaction is completed.</p>
</li>

<li><p><strong>Online:</strong> Ricktag Points will not be issued for every dollar spent online. However, from time to time, bonus Ricktag Points may be awarded for purchases made online, as advertised by Ricktag on <a href="http://www.ricktag.ca/">www.ricktag.ca/</a> and/or in-stores. Also, Members can be, from time to time, eligible to receive a "Member Discount" on any participating Ricktag Merchants, as advertised by Ricktag from time to time at <a href="http://www.ricktag.ca/">www.ricktag.ca/</a></p></li>

<li><p>Ricktag Points may be awarded retroactively if the original receipt and your Ricktag Rewards Card is produced in-stores within 14 days of the date of the original Eligible Purchase.</p></li>

<li><p>Ricktag Points will be awarded at the rate decided by the Merchant which will be listed on <a href="http://www.ricktag.ca/">www.ricktag.ca</a>. Ricktag Points for each dollar spent on Eligible Purchases. Ricktag Points will be calculated by reference to the net (Eligible Purchase price less discounts) pre-tax total on each cash register receipt. Ricktag may offer special promotions from time to time offering additional Ricktag Points(“bonus Ricktag  points”). Such bonus Ricktag points, once awarded, shall form part of the Member’s Ricktag Points balance (the Ricktag Points and bonus Ricktag Points collectively referred to as “Ricktag Points”).</p></li>

<li><p>All Ricktag Points awarded for an Eligible Purchase as well as the Member’s current Ricktag Points balance can be found in you’re My Account page at www.ricktag.ca. In the event of a discrepancy our internal database and records will govern. Occasionally, through specified promotions by participating Stores and/or Program Partners, additional Ricktag Points(and/or other rewards or benefits) may be awarded for using the Ricktag Rewards Card, or for being a Member.</p></li> 

<li><p>Ricktag’s standard Return/Exchange Policy applies. In the event of a return/exchange of any Eligible Purchase, Ricktag Points will be deducted automatically from the Account that was used for the Eligible Purchase (whether or not the Ricktag Rewards Card is presented at the time of return and/or exchange). </p></li>

<li><p>All Ricktag Points totals, will be deemed correct unless otherwise substantiated by the Member by bringing forward evidence satisfactory to Ricktag. In the case of a discrepancy, our internal database and records govern. Discrepancies must be addressed with the Ricktag Rewards Customer Service Centre within three months of the date on which the discrepancy occurred. Ricktag reserves the right to restrict redemption or put a “hold” on Ricktag Points for up to 90 days from the date the points are posted to an Account if Ricktag has reasonable belief that fraud has occurred or in the event of a breach or suspected breach of the Terms and Conditions of this Program.</p></li>

<li><p>Ricktag Points are not transferable from one Member to another. Ricktag may, however, in its sole discretion allow the transfer of Ricktag Points in accordance with the “transfer points” terms and conditions posted from time to time at <a href="http://www.ricktag.ca/">www.ricktag.ca</a></p></li>

<li><p>Ricktag Points are reduced to zero upon closure of a Ricktag rewards membership.</p></li>

<li><p>Upon the death of a Member, the Member’s account will be closed and any Ricktag Points in the account will be forfeited. Ricktag Points are not divisible in the case of divorce.</p></li>

<li><p>Should any Member not collect Ricktag Points using a Ricktag Rewards Card or redeem Ricktag Points for 12 consecutive calendar months, the membership will be deemed to be inactive and all accumulated Ricktag Points will be forfeited. If a Member’s only activity in 12 consecutive calendar months consists of transferring points under any Ricktag promotion in existence from time to time, the membership will be deemed inactive and all accumulated Ricktag Points will be forfeited.</p></li>

